<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>348</hymn_number>
<title>&quot;RESTING IN THE EVERLASTING ARMS&quot;</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw kivawp khawmna, Aw ka kipahna,
 A kumsawt, venbitna a chawl in;
 Aw vangsakna lul Pathien lungmuonna,
 A kumsawt venbitna a chawlin!

[V2]
 Chawlin, chawlin,
 Lauhum cheng apat a bitin;
 Chawlin, chawlin
 A kumsawt venbitna a chawlin.

[V3]
 2. Ka khuolzinna ah bittak in ka um,
 A kumsawt venbitna a chawlin;
 Ka lampi ni chengin a vak zing hi,
 A kumsawt venbitna a chawlin.

[V4]
 3. Banga ka gin ding, bang ka lauh ding?
 A kumsawt venbitna a chawlin;
 Hukdampa a nai, muonna kim ka nei,
 A kumsawt venbitna a chawlin.</lyrics>
</song>